	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S[alutem] d[ico].</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accipe hic, <persName ref="person19">Ambrosi</persName>, frater suavissime, quae respondi <persName ref="person640">Cochleo</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Siehe oben <ref target="file11885">Nr. 1839</ref>, Anm. 3; 1858, Anm. 1; unten 1870.</note>, ac iudica libere fratremque admone liberrime.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi haec intra septimanas fere 14 horis succisivis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Defendi causam communem, atque utinam magno cum fructu!</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae his tuis coniunxi, quaeso <placeName ref="place1113">Ulmam</placeName> ad <persName ref="person64">Frechtum</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="person64">Martin Frecht</persName>. - Ein Brief Bullingers an Frecht ist nicht erhalten.</note> deferri diligenter curato.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dono illum exemplari; sed et literas a me <persName ref="person640">Cochleo</persName> scriptas<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Eine Abschrift dieses Briefes unten <ref target="file11916">Nr. 1870</ref>.</note> una cum exemplari mitto rogans, ut ipsa fide bona ad <persName ref="person640">Cochleum</persName> deferri curet<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Zur Übermittlung dieser Schrift durch <persName ref="person64">Frecht</persName> s. <persName ref="person19">Blarer</persName> BW II 267 sowie unten <ref target="file11975">Nr. 1928</ref>; s. auch den Brief Bullingers an Vadian, oben <ref target="file11907">Nr. 1861</ref>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nolo, ut responsio per omnium oberret manus, priusquam ad ipsum perveniat, ad quem pertinet maxime.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nolo illius imitari exemplum, qui scribit ad me ac vulgat libellum<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Gemeint ist <persName ref="person640">Cochläus</persName>' Schrift gegen Bullinger; s. oben <ref target="file11885">Nr. 1839</ref>, Anm. 2.</note>, non autem mittit<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Bullinger erwähnt dies auch im Brief an <persName ref="person640">Cochläus</persName> selbst; s. unten <ref target="file11916">Nr. 1870</ref>, 2f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nec causam agens optimam tantillum metuo.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In luce palam et aperto Marte<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Vgl. Seneca, Oedipus, 275.</note> agere ac congredi cupio, ago et congredior.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si ille referire perrexerit, clypeum non abiiciam, modo gloriae dei et ecclesiarum saluti conducere putavero.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura iam non possum.<pb type="edition" next="136"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora pro me dominum.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Undique pericula et tentationes; sed liberabit ex his dominus.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum clarissimo fratre tuo<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="person20">Thomas Blarer</persName>.</note>, Zviccio<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><persName ref="person264">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note> atque reliquis.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Martii 14., anno domini 1544.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">H. Bullingerus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="person19">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, amico incomparabili, fratri honorando et semper charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
